title: Food Pack Asia 2021
description: Food Pack Asia 2021, the 12th international food processing, drink technology and packaging exhibition. Showcasing latest technology and innovations of food processing, packaging technology, confectionery machinery, hotel and restaurant equipment from more than 350. Food Pack Asia 2021 is going to take place on April 7-10, 2021 at Bangkok International Trade and Exhibition Center (BITEC, Bangkok)
